{
  "stem": "14251.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at that point, she had been moved from Terezin, Theresienstadt to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Husband had been gassed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Father had died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she knew-- had it all down correct.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Didn't know she had married, but knew her married name now and had been on the foot march to Belsen, Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is where they met, with the barbed wire between them, because the other lady in error was put in a Dutch children's camp with her five-year-old son.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she said, the war is almost over, because she had just come there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She had been underground all this time in Berlin and was only lastly caught in December, '44 and said, you've got to hang on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the-- my mother's sister said, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I know I'm dying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I just re-read this before you came to refresh my mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it's useless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Everybody's dead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My sister is dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My husband's been gassed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody's dead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "No, I can't do this anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were carrying a tree trunk on their shoulders, she and another woman, according to that letter, for whatever senseless reason.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the woman, whose name was [NON-ENGLISH], who is now named Murray, said she ordered her to come to that same fence tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Meet me tomorrow here, trying to give her incentive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she said, no, I won't be.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she, she went back day after day after day and never saw her again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So we assumed that she was one of the, one of the people you saw later at Belsen, strewn on the grounds, I would guess.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my mother is tough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I feel nothing special about me, nor did a god save me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think it was luck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because you see, a bomb could have hit us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
